<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-599-968  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 599 968.andO;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Network World  June 25 1990 v7 n26 p6(1).andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>MCI airs service package aimed at smaller users. (MCICommunications Corp.'s MCI Vision)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Messmer, Ellen.andM;</AUTHOR><TEXT><ABSTRACT>MCI Communications Corp is offering a new outbound long-distanceservices package, MCI Vision, which is aimed at medium to smallsized companies spending up to $50,000 on monthly services.andP;  Theflat-rate pricing structure includes features such as consolidatedbilling and volume discounts for spending at multiple locations.andO;MCI has traditionally provided these features for large businesscustomers only.andP;  MCI Vision calls made between 8 AM and 5 PM, peakhours, cost 15 cents per minute over dedicated access facilitiesand 20 cents per minute over switched access routes.andP;  Off-peakcalls are discounted at 20 percent off the normal per minute rate.andO;Volume discounts of up to 20 percent are possible with monthlyspending of $30,000.andM;</ABSTRACT></TEXT><DESCRIPT>Company:   MCI Communications Corp. (services).andO;Ticker:    MCIC.andO;Topic:     Communications Service SuppliersCost of CommunicationsTelecommunicationsTelephone Companies.andM;</DESCRIPT></DOC>